title: [SOLVED]820-00165 liqued damage
message: Pre fucked so it can be corrosion anywhere. Inspect closer, but it could be corrosion under any chip or corroded resistor trace. Check the usual suspects, U1900/50,U6100 termination resistors, TON resistors on CPU regulator, crap under SMC, etc.
